<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>POLL</title>
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/TextPlugin.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="light-theme"> 
    
    <div class="noise-bg"></div>
    <div class="scanline"></div>
    <canvas id="scribble-canvas"></canvas>

    <div class="cursor-main"></div>
    <div class="cursor-outline"></div>

    <div class="hud hud-top-left">
        SYNC: <span id="sync-progress">0</span>%<br>
        STAGE: <span id="stage-counter">0/50</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hud hud-bottom-right">
        MEMORY: <span id="hud-mem">69</span>%<br>
        UID: <span class="blink">6666966080409090210</span>
    </div>

    <div class="marquee-container">
        <div class="marquee-content">
            /// 123456 /// POLL /// 50 /// QUESTION /// SYSTEM ///
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="theme-switcher magnetic" onclick="toggleTheme()">
        INV_THEME
    </div>

    <div class="transition-flash"></div>

    <main class="viewport">
        <div id="quiz-content" class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="intro-sequence">
                <h1 class="glitch-title" data-text="DEEP_SCAN_50">POLL_OT_MENYA</h1>
                <div class="line-separator"></div>
                <p class="deep-text">это мой опрос для тебя чтобы узнать о тебе больше. тут 50 вопросов. не перезагружай страницу когда будешь проходить<br>нажми на <span class="blink">START_POLL</span> когда будешь готова</p>
                <button class="mega-btn magnetic" onclick="startAdvancedQuiz()">
                    START_POLL
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>